  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the guy-- the commandant of the Swedish transport-- goes over to the-- to the officer and says, please remove your troops from this spot here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are neutral, we are under orders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The guy says, what are you, crazy?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I don't want to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the guy says-- so the commandant says-- and this is-- I don't know how they could be that-- that-- that correct, but this guy says, well, if you don't I have to call Himmler, Vice Fuhrer Himmler, and tell him that you will not obey his orders.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when he heard that, the guy took off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he could have-- at that time, you know, this is like 10, 15 days before the war is over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were shooting people for no reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He could have taken-- he could have turned around, let's wipe this convoy out and nobody would have known any different.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in the meantime, he got away with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went the next day, we crossed the Danish border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for-- I don't know how did Danes find out about it, but all of a sudden, there's people standing on the streets with flowers and-- and-- and now, there was also a German commandant on this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he says-- he says to the Swedish guy, if this does not stop, we will return.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll turn around and go back to-- so they got hold of some of the Danish people there and says, look, got to stop and please call down the line that we can't have that kind of-- kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next-- that same evening-- that same afternoon, I think, we arrive in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
